title: Was Suspect César Sayuk working at the same sector club as Stormy Daniels to prove Hawks' conspiracy?
subtitle: The conspiracy theorists misunderstand the details in an attempt to link Sayuk to one of President Donald Trump's main suspects.
author: Dan MacGuill
vclaim: Cesar Sayuk and Stormy Daniels worked at the same Florida strip club, suggesting or proving their parts in a conspiracy theory against Trump.
